#### **9. `src/setup-surface.ts`**

UI wizard for onboarding (prompts user for config):

```typescript
import type { ChannelSetupWizard } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/setup";

export const [channel]SetupWizard: ChannelSetupWizard = async (params) => {
  const { cfg, accountId, prompter, log } = params;

