## 7. RUNTIME MANAGEMENT (src/runtime.ts)

### Universal Pattern:
```typescript
import { createPluginRuntimeStore } from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/runtime-store";
import type { PluginRuntime } from "./runtime-api.js";

const { setRuntime: set[ChannelName]Runtime, getRuntime: get[ChannelName]Runtime } =
  createPluginRuntimeStore<PluginRuntime>("[Channel] runtime not initialized");

export { get[ChannelName]Runtime, set[ChannelName]Runtime };
export function clear[ChannelName]Runtime() {
  set[ChannelName]Runtime(undefined as unknown as PluginRuntime);
}
```

This provides a simple singleton pattern for accessing runtime state across the plugin.

